sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Learner
    participant Landing as Landing Page
    participant Auth as Auth System
    participant Dashboard as Dashboard Layout
    participant Content as Dashboard Content
    participant DB as Database/API

    User->>Landing: Visits Homepage
    Landing->>User: Display Hero, Features, How-It-Works
    User->>Landing: Clicks "Get Started" / "Login"
    Landing->>Auth: Open Login Modal
    User->>Auth: Enters Credentials
    Auth->>DB: Validate User
    DB-->>Auth: User Verified
    Auth-->>User: Auth Token
    Auth->>Dashboard: Redirect to /learner-dashboard
    Dashboard->>Content: Render LearnerDashboardContent
    Content->>DB: Fetch Progress/Stats
    DB-->>Content: Return Data
    Content-->>User: Display Monitoring Dashboard
    
    par Parallel Actions
        User->>Content: View Progress Cards
        User->>Content: Click Quick Actions (Practice)
        User->>Content: Check Recent Activity
    end
